## USER RESEARCH

**Top 5 Pain Points**
1. Non-dominant hand designs come out messy and uneven — users feel the skill gap is insurmountable
2. Nail art looks amazing online but turns out blotchy, smudged, or blobby at home — polish consistency issues
3. No idea what tools are actually needed vs. just nice-to-have; overwhelmed by product lists
4. Designs chip within 1–2 days at home vs. 2 weeks at the salon — prep and top coat skipped
5. Tutorials show fast-forward videos with zero explanation of how to hold the brush or achieve clean edges

**User Sentiment:** Aspirational but frustrated — users want to replicate what they see on TikTok and want permission to start imperfectly and still get results.

